  ",["BUTTON",{"type":"submit","class":"button","name":"submit"},"Select"],"\n",["INPUT",{"__playwright_value_":"CfDJ8NtNJeIAnopNploEY98x4GWsPnJQQP-5DZKtNkcqC8Ehhe7dVIC20xQ1WMMCI3f4rPWyIBFH2N0-UvJi0LdslqufVZA0GTteAKgnrpgAvMRoMucOWEmUYJIiXDIDla5MeclTXlPurmigL00wEBAVLF0","name":"__RequestVerificationToken","type":"hidden","value":"CfDJ8NtNJeIAnopNploEY98x4GWsPnJQQP-5DZKtNkcqC8Ehhe7dVIC20xQ1WMMCI3f4rPWyIBFH2N0-UvJi0LdslqufVZA0GTteAKgnrpgAvMRoMucOWEmUYJIiXDIDla5MeclTXlPurmigL00wEBAVLF0"}],["INPUT",{"__playwright_value_":"CfDJ8NtNJeIAnopNploEY98x4GXMZk_IYE5ftaohPJ8QpwkzvasWwuktBCRCOiMUDoD0UdC5l-zlgH2_V7HqELubEvxHPswjHuN8l5uFXyWiqYrte3YIhZerj1tDuwiIy6vWW7MRK9pJxgXYZsCbWHxsukXSIrnL4weYe1PTXUwB5W-K","name":"ufprt","type":"hidden","value":"CfDJ8NtNJeIAnopNploEY98x4GXMZk_IYE5ftaohPJ8QpwkzvasWwuktBCRCOiMUDoD0UdC5l-zlgH2_V7HqELubEvxHPswjHuN8l5uFXyWiqYrte3YIhZerj1tDuwiIy6vWW7MRK9pJxgXYZsCbWHxsukXSIrnL4weYe1PTXUwB5W-K"}]],"\n    \n"],"\n                                            "],"\n                            "],"\n                            ",["DIV",{"class":"grid-x grid-padding-x"},"\n                                            ",["DIV",{"class":"cell content-text"},"\n                                                \n\n\n",["P",{},"If you have signed up for our ",["A",{"data-udi":"umb://document/023238180a634fccac66dfaee1db0bfb","href":"/waste-recycling/garden-waste/","title":"Garden Waste"},"garden waste collection service"]," you can also use this form to find your collection day."],"\n\n\n                                            "],"\n                            "],"\n                            ",["DIV",{"class":"grid-x grid-padding-x"},"\n                                            ",["DIV",{"class":"cell content-text"},"\n                                                \n\n\n",["H3",{},"Collection information"],"\n",["P",{},"Collections take place between 7am and 3pm. Place your bins at the edge of your property ready for collection from 7am on collection day. Bin lids must be closed."],"\n",["P",{},"Recycling should be clean, dry, loose and not in bags. Find more details on our ",["A",{"data-udi":"umb://document/646dbdf198d04e98966c237e52f34d04","href":"/waste-recycling/kerbside-recycling-in-mid-sussex/","title":"Recycling in Mid Sussex"},"recycling page"],"."],"\n",["P",{},"Please note, the bin calendar only shows the next four bin collections from your property, however, collection dates repeat in the same pattern throughout the year. The only exception is at Christmas and New Year which is subject to temporary changes."],"\n\n\n                                            "],"\n                            "],"\n                "],"\n                ",["DIV",{"class":"content-row ","id":"79a4f618-dc33-0e45-6fd8-d23faed62454"},"\n                            ",["DIV",{"class":"grid-x grid-padding-x"},"\n                                            ",["DIV",{"class":"cell content-header","data-magellan-target":"topic-missed-bins","id":"topic-missed-bins"},"\n                                                \n\n\n        ",["H2",{},"Missed bins"],"\n    \n\n                                            "],"\n                            "],"\n                            ",["DIV",{"class":"grid-x grid-padding-x"},"\n                                            ",["DIV",{"class":"cell content-text"},"\n                                                \n\n\n",["H3",{},"Before you report a missed bin"],"\n",["P",{},"If your rubbish, recycling or garden waste collection has been missed, please check the following:"],"\n",["UL",{},"\n",["LI",{},["STRONG",{},"Day"]," - have you put your bins out on the right day? You can check the bin collection calendar above"],"\n",["LI",{},["STRONG",{},"Position"]," - Are your bins at the edge of your property? Are they in a clearly visible location?"],"\n",["LI",{},["STRONG",{},"Container"]," - Are you using bins provided by Mid Sussex District Council? If not your rubbish will not be collected"],"\n",["LI",{},["STRONG",{},"Time"]," - were your bins ready for collection from 7am?\n",["UL",{},"\n",["LI",{},"Collections take place between ",["STRONG",{},"7am "],"and ",["STRONG",{},"3pm"],". Please don't report a missed bin until after 3pm on your usual collection day as it ",["STRONG",{},"may be collected any time until 3pm"],"."],"\n"],"\n"],"\n"],"\n",["P",{},["STRONG",{},"We won't collect if"]],"\n",["UL",{},"\n",["LI",{},"Your rubbish, recycling or garden waste isn’t available to collect from 7am"],"\n",["LI",{},"Your recycling bin contains items we can’t recycle"],"\n",["LI",{},"Your rubbish bin contains garden waste. Garden waste can be taken to a household waste recycling site or we offer a ",["A",{"data-udi":"umb://document/023238180a634fccac66dfaee1db0bfb","href":"/waste-recycling/garden-waste/","title":"Garden Waste"},"garden waste collection service"]],"\n",["LI",{},"Your bin is over-full"],"\n",["LI",{},"The contents of your bin are stuck, due to freezing conditions or jammed material"],"\n",["LI",{},"The road is blocked or access has been hindered in some way"],"\n"],"\n",["H3",{},"Frozen garden bins"],"\n",["P",{},"Frozen garden bins can be damaged by the collection lorry. If your bin freezes during very cold weather it may not be collected for safety reasons."],"\n",["P",{},"We will return later in the day if possible."],"\n",["P",{},"If we are unable to empty your bins we will return on the next scheduled collection day."],"\n",["P",{},"Please read our ",["SPAN",{"style":"text-decoration: underline;"},["A",{"data-udi":"umb://media/8567ccc2de3e416ea13550e46a8664f5","href":"/media/1722/garden-waste-terms-and-conditions.pdf","title":"garden waste terms and conditions"},"Garden Waste Collection Service Terms and Conditions"," (254 KB, PDF) ",["svg",{"aria-hidden":"true","class":"svg-inline--fa fa-file-pdf","focusable":"false","data-prefix":"fas","data-icon":"file-pdf","role":"img","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","viewBox":"0 0 512 512","data-fa-i2svg":""},["path",{"fill":"currentColor","d":"M0 64C0 28.7 28.7 0 64 0L224 0l0 128c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32l128 0 0 144-208 0c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64l0 144-48 0c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64L0 64zm384 64l-128 0L256 0 384 128zM176 352l32 0c30.9 0 56 25.1 56 56s-25.1 56-56 56l-16 0 0 32c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16s-16-7.2-16-16l0-48 0-80c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16zm32 80c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24l-16 0 0 48 16 0zm96-80l32 0c26.5 0 48 21.5 48 48l0 64c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48l-32 0c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16l0-128c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16zm32 128c8.8 0 16-7.2 16-16l0-64c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16l-16 0 0 96 16 0zm80-112c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16l48 0c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16s-7.2 16-16 16l-32 0 0 32 32 0c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16s-7.2 16-16 16l-32 0 0 48c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16s-16-7.2-16-16l0-64 0-64z"}]]],"."]],"\n",["H3",{},"How to report a missed bin"],"\n",["P",{},"If you followed the above guidelines and your bins were still not collected, please ",["A",{"href":"https://online.midsussex.gov.uk/article/1074/","title":"Report a missed bin online"},"fill in our online Missed Bin Collection form"," ",["svg",{"aria-hidden":"true","class":"svg-inline--fa fa-up-right-from-square","aria-labelledby":"svg-inline--fa-title-NhIC7Wvw5dvq","data-prefix":"fas","data-icon":"up-right-from-square","role":"img","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","viewBox":"0 0 512 512","data-fa-i2svg":""},["title",{"id":"svg-inline--fa-title-NhIC7Wvw5dvq"},"leave this site"],["path",{"fill":"currentColor","d":"M352 0c-12.9 0-24.6 7.8-29.6 19.8s-2.2 25.7 6.9 34.9L370.7 96 201.4 265.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3s32.8 12.5 45.3 0L416 141.3l41.4 41.4c9.2 9.2 22.9 11.9 34.9 6.9s19.8-16.6 19.8-29.6l0-128c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32L352 0zM80 32C35.8 32 0 67.8 0 112L0 432c0 44.2 35.8 80 80 80l320 0c44.2 0 80-35.8 80-80l0-112c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 112c0 8.8-7.2 16-16 16L80 448c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16l0-320c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16l112 0c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32L80 32z"}]]],". This should be done as soon as possible."],"\n\n\n                                          